<BaseLayout title="Computer Networks · Virtual Labs · AquinTutor" description="Six computing experiments: IP subnetting, the TCP three-way handshake state machine, Go-Back-N and Selective-Repeat sliding windows, Dijkstra and Bellman-Ford routing, CRC and Hamming error control, and CIDR aggregation.">
